                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-82-off466 t18290910-82-cd467"></join>, 3 half-crowns, 1 sixpence, and 1 farthing, the monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290910-82-victim824" type="victimName">
